{
    "maqras": [
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "He frowned and turned away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "because the blind man came to him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "And what would apprise thee? Perhaps he would purify himself"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "or be reminded, such that the reminder might benefit him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "As for him who deems himself beyond need"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "to him dost thou attend"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "though thou art not answerable, should he not be purified"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "But as for him who came to thee striving earnestly"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "while fearful"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "from him thou art diverted"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "Nay! Truly it is a reminder—"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "so let whomsoever will, remember it—"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "on pages honored"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "exalted and purified"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "in the hands of scribes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "noble and pious"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "May man perish! How ungrateful is he"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "From what thing did He create him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "From a drop He created him, then proportioned him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "then He made the way easy for him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "Then He caused him to die and buried him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Then, when He willed, He resurrected him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "Nay! But he has not accomplished what He commanded him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "So let man consider his food"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "that We pour down water in abundance"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "then We split the earth in fissures"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "and cause grains to grow therein"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "and vines and herbs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "and olives and date palms"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "and gardens densely planted"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 31,
            "text": "and fruit and pastures"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 32,
            "text": "as sustenance for you and for your flocks"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 33,
            "text": "So when the Piercing Cry does come"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 34,
            "text": "that Day when a man will flee from his brother"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 35,
            "text": "and his mother and his father"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 36,
            "text": "and his spouse and his children"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 37,
            "text": "For every man that Day his affair shall suffice him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 38,
            "text": "Faces that Day shall be shining, radiant"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 39,
            "text": "laughing, joyous"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 40,
            "text": "And faces that Day shall be covered with dust"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 41,
            "text": "overspread with darkness"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 42,
            "text": "Those, they are the disbelievers, the profligates"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "When the sun is enfolded"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "and when the stars fade away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "when the mountains are set in motion"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "and when pregnant camels are abandoned"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "when the wild beasts are gathered"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "and when the seas are made to swell over"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "when the souls are coupled"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "and when the female infant buried alive is asked"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "for what sin she was slain"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "when the pages are spread"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "and when Heaven is laid bare"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "when Hellfire is kindled"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "and when the Garden is brought nigh"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "each soul shall know what it has made ready"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "So I swear by those receding"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "those that move and set"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "by the night as it approaches"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "and by the morning as it breathes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "Truly it is the speech of a noble messenger"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "possessed of strength, before the Possessor of the Throne, of high rank"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "obeyed, trustworthy withal"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Your companion is not possessed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "He surely saw him upon the clear horizon"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "And he does not withhold grudgingly the Unseen"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Nor is it the speech of a satan outcast"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "So where are you going"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "It is naught but a reminder for the worlds"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "for those of you who will to go straight"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "And you do not will but that God, Lord of the worlds, wills"
        }
    ]
}